<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">
<html>
<head>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
	<div class='title'>
		Welcome
	</div>
	
	<div class='text'>
		In the following task you have to decide as quickly as possible whether the font color of the words 
		presented is green or blue.
	</div>
	<br><br>
	<div class='text'>
		Press <span class='highlight_red'>A</span> on your keyboard if the font color is green; press 
		<span class='highlight_red'>L</span> on your keyboard if the font color is blue. <br><br>
		If a green check mark appears in the upper right corner, your decision was correct, otherwise a red cross will be displayed. 
		Press the escape key (ESC) on your keyboard to exit the training at any time.<br><br>
	</div>
	
	<div class='text'>
		Start with the <span class='highlight_red'>right arrow</span> on your keyboard.
	</div>
</body>
</html>